{"tid":2307133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防疫措施累死舞台劇 -梁祖堯以抗爭和警暴為題舞台劇被腰斬","createTime":"2020-12-01T03:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T12:10:28.000Z","uid":48124,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"21ce20a64d273ef6486824987f139fcb575e996a","tid":2307133,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:33:43.000Z","msg":"由梁祖堯擔任創作總監兼聯同卓韻芝、湯駿業、邵美君同陳曙曦主演嘅風車草劇團舞台劇《新聞小花的告白2白屋之夏》，之前因為疫情兩度延期，一直延遲至上個月27號先喺葵青劇院開騷，演出共14場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vUR8Ux4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvUR8Ux4.jpg&h=049ed7c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5tfzx5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5tfzx5.png&h=45c7340a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前晚演出到第五場，但林鄭噚日下晝宣佈由聽日（周三）起收緊防疫措施，政府表演場地要關閉兩星期，祖堯嘅舞台劇演出場數都未到一半就突然要cut，咁觀眾買咗飛點算？演員點算？製作費又點算？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HK7TmcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHK7TmcR.jpg&h=8338c420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭日前做傳媒訪問時，被問到造成社會動盪，佢話冇內疚仲反問「我做錯了甚麼？」祖堯噚晩就忍唔住喺社交媒體爆「我哋又做錯過甚麼」！<br />\n<br />\n祖堯真係好嬲，佢喺fb話：「我哋已做好所有可以嘅安全措施，但最終還是敵不過這個政府後知後覺。佈景，起咗。服裝，買咗。所有工作人員嘅努力，已經付出咗。飛。賣咗。14場，到呢一刻只係做咗5場。而林鄭啱啱話，冇準備推出新一輪嘅紓困措施。呢個巨大嘅損失，我哋將要自己承擔。我都想問。我。哋。又。做。錯。過。甚。麼。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日凌晨風車草劇團公佈，已買餘下場次嘅退款安排將稍後公佈，但劇團臨時加開今日（12月1日）下午3點嘅特別場，劃一賣四百蚊，現場購買同劃位，但唔可以用其他場次換飛，而賣飛時間由中午12點開始。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">稍後仲可能會有online版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附上觀眾評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UdwT5E1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUdwT5E1.png&h=8ecc33f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mm4RSj1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmm4RSj1.png&h=bf2ff598&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qY5d5E1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqY5d5E1.png&h=ee632b15&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHQd5E2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHQd5E2.png&h=178f37b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4a72f7539f81f359886749f230601f52d340de4","tid":2307133,"uid":197637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"推 希望買左飛既人 無得睇都唔好退"},{"pid":"6b0cbb7375e0cb2153e80cbe44039051468a2421","tid":2307133,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6deaf899a5e941b4da8ee833dea00f8214dc56e2","tid":2307133,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"防疫措施擺明玩針對<br />\n出刀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d0c701132752cce99f3725b5794412a3713a08","tid":2307133,"uid":296600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:07:08.000Z","msg":"好想睇<br />\n網上開場得唔得？"},{"pid":"4ce10693245b044695c3942b7ace2ae7aaa86701","tid":2307133,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"阿祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}